<p>I want to use imagemagick/im4java to combine two images into a single image -</p>  <p>I have a command that works great in command line.</p>  <pre><code>'composite -gravity center -geometry +25+0 image1.png -compose multiply                                                    image2.png output.png` </code></pre>  <p>I want to achieve the same results using im4java.core package, I have this set of commands but it does not give me the right result.</p>  <pre><code>CompositeCmd composite = new CompositeCmd() IMOperation operation = new IMOperation(); operation.gravity("center") operation.geometry(25,0) operation.addImage() operation.compose("multiply") operation.addImage() operation.addImage()  composite.run(operation, "image1.png","image2.png", "output3.png") </code></pre>